Package: influxr
Type: Package
Title: R Wrapper For Influx V2 API
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Danny Merchant
Maintainer: Danny Merchant <dmerchant@camgian.com>
Description: The influxr package provides an R interface to an Influx database through the V2 API.
    An influx connection object tracks the database's connection endpoint, the organization, 
    and the authorization token.  Table streams returned from flux queries are automatically 
    parsed as tidyverse tibbles.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
